// history of geology (Hutton, Lyell, Darwin). The lesson data itself lays out
// competing frameworks fairly. This guide stays pastoral and non-polemical:
// we do not referee young-earth vs. old-earth here. We help mom stay calm,
// keep the focus on the Creator, and model honest observation over anxiety.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

